Purchasing Premium TTF, OTF, WOFF, EOT, and SVG Files

If you're interested in our premium font and SVG files, here's how...

Find the premium file you wish to purchase from our collection.
Click the "Buy Now" button.
Follow the instructions to send the payment using the provided methods.
Provide us with the transaction code or a screenshot of the payment confirmation.
Once confirmed, you will receive the file via email.

We strive to make the process smooth and efficient.

Why Choose Our Font and SVG Files?

Our website offers a wide variety of high-quality fonts (TTF, OTF, WOFF, EOT) and scalable vector graphics (SVG) to enhance your creative projects.

Have Questions?

If you have any questions, please visit our Support Page.

`;

        if (type === "mobile") {
            if (selectedMainFormat === 'Fonts') {
                specificContent = `


  How To Import Fonts In Pixellab And DesignLab

${commonFontContent}
`;
            } else { // PLP, IPV, JPG, PNG for Mobile
                specificContent = `










    How to Import PLP IPV File?







    How to Download?







